Model Exploration

Daniel Chen

Univariate

fit <- lm(rank ~ week, data = clean_out)
(coefs <- tidy(fit))
## # A tibble: 2 x 5
##   term        estimate std.error statistic   p.value
##   <chr>          <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl>
## 1 (Intercept)    64.1     0.602      106.  0.       
## 2 week           -1.14    0.0413     -27.6 7.41e-157
ggplot(coefs, aes(x = estimate, y = term)) +
    geom_point() +
    geom_errorbarh(aes(xmin = std.error - (1.96 * estimate),
                       xmax = std.error + (1.96 * estimate))) +
    theme_minimal()

ggsave(here('./output/billboard_model_plots/coefs_predict_rank_week.png'),
       width = 8, height = 5, units = 'in')
ggplot(coefs[!coefs$term %in% c('(Intercept)'), ], aes(x = estimate, y = term)) +
    geom_point() +
    geom_errorbarh(aes(xmin = std.error - (1.96 * estimate),
                       xmax = std.error + (1.96 * estimate))) +
    theme_minimal()

ggsave(here('./output/billboard_model_plots/coefs_predict_rank_week_no_intercept.png'),
       width = 8, height = 5, units = 'in')

Multiple

fit <- lm(rank ~ week + artist, data = clean_out)
(coefs <- tidy(fit))
## # A tibble: 229 x 5
##    term                 estimate std.error statistic  p.value
##    <chr>                   <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl>    <dbl>
##  1 (Intercept)            87.6      7.71      11.4   1.51e-29
##  2 week                   -0.534    0.0369   -14.5   1.35e-46
##  3 artist2Ge+her           3.50    14.1        0.249 8.03e- 1
##  4 artist3 Doors Down    -38.0      8.10      -4.69  2.83e- 6
##  5 artist504 Boyz        -26.3      9.08      -2.89  3.85e- 3
##  6 artist98?             -44.3      8.96      -4.95  7.81e- 7
##  7 artistA*Teens          11.0     11.9        0.924 3.55e- 1
##  8 artistAaliyah         -49.7      8.22      -6.05  1.55e- 9
##  9 artistAdams, Yolanda  -14.2      8.96      -1.59  1.13e- 1
## 10 artistAdkins, Trace    -8.09     9.86      -0.820 4.12e- 1
## # ... with 219 more rows
ggplot(coefs, aes(x = estimate,
                  y = term)) +
    geom_point() +
    geom_errorbarh(aes(xmin = std.error - (1.96 * estimate),
                       xmax = std.error + (1.96 * estimate))) +
    theme_minimal()

ggsave(here('./output/billboard_model_plots/coefs_predict_rank_week_artist.png'),
       width = 8, height = 5, units = 'in')
ggplot(coefs[!coefs$term %in% c('(Intercept)'), ],
       aes(x = estimate,
           y = fct_reorder(term, estimate))) +
    geom_point() +
    theme_minimal()

ggsave(here('./output/billboard_model_plots/coefs_predict_rank_week_artist_sorted.png'),
       width = 8, height = 5, units = 'in')
